<h2>What We Collect and Receive</h2>
<p>
    In order for you to create an account on @ViewData["AppName"] and use our Services, we need to collect and process certain information. Depending on your use of the Services, that may include:
</p>

<p>
    <ul>
        <li>Information you provide by completing forms on @ViewData["AppName"] - your name, email and postal addresses, telephone number, country of residence, login, and password details. We may ask for this information if you register as a user of the Services, subscribe to our newsletters, upload or submit content through @ViewData["AppName"], or if you contact us;</li>
