        <li>Information about the ways people visit and interact with our Site, in the form of traffic analytics.</li>
        <li>Communications you send to us (for example, when you ask for support, send us questions or comments, or report a problem);</li>
        <li>Information that you submit on or to @ViewData["AppName"] in the form of comments, contributions to discussions, or messages to other users.</li>
        <li>You may decline to provide us with your information. However, this will limit your ability to register for an account or use our Services. You may review, change or remove your information through your account settings.</li>
    </ul>
</p>

